main event: A UFO was observed in Killeen, Texas on the night of September 17, 1967.
interesting points: The object appeared as a light, described as being brighter than the brightest star,The sighting lasted from 8:10 PM to 8:30 PM, with the object moving slowly and changing direction sharply,Observers reported a small white object circling quickly around the UFO during its descent,The UFO faded out after its movements, The report lacked photographs and relied on handwritten and typed descriptions.
sighted object: a bright light in the sky
witness description: a 13-year-old male who observed the phenomenon
